{"tid":498344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女司機技驚四座  4線轉彎唔夠位直撼警車","createTime":"2017-12-13T16:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T06:23:45.000Z","uid":5195,"like":322,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":124,"replies":[{"pid":"d7842b45eaf4149e8b5dc7a17745d0ea01e537e8","tid":498344,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T16:34:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171213/photo/bkn-20171213184408760-1213_00822_001_02b.jpg?20171213194057\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171213%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171213184408760-1213_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20171213194057&h=70871946&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n周三（13日）早上9時許，一輛黃色小型私家車在大埔安慈路，鄰近翠屏商場位置，與停泊避車處的一輛警車發生輕微相撞。有網民笑稱，「史上最快報警方法」！<br />\n<br />\n涉事意外被網民拍下，並分享至多個社交群組上，據現場圖片可見，該私家車車頭正面向警車車身，兩者非常貼近，而私家車的左邊車門則留有多條黑色刮痕。<br />\n<br />\n有自稱目擊事發經過的網民稱：「（司機）扭咗好多手，跟住就見停喺恒生出面架警車有sir落車、見影晒相先知係撞到」。其後，有多輛警車到場協助調查。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民均取笑涉事私家車司機駕駛技術不精，「4條線其實應該幾好turn」、 「細車仔，四條線，一手軚正常人都轉到」、「撞擊測試合格」！<br />\n<br />\n警方回覆《港呢啲》查詢表示，涉事女司機姓郭，當時駕駛該私家車由安慈路3號一停車場駛出，當右轉入安慈路一線時，突撞到避車處的警車。意外中沒有人受傷，司機酒精測試為零度。"},{"pid":"6aff827af49c3abb25e47228d212f116d21b96e5","tid":498344,"uid":85097,"like":374,"dislike":1,"score":373,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T16:37:40.000Z","msg":"佢當年點考窄路掉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c57555479bdfd0122ab70c99b4fa40320a134ad","tid":498344,"uid":89514,"like":1062,"dislike":3,"score":1059,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T16:40:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"22afa0ac92fdd87768cd9fb9d5b37fc978f5b68c","tid":498344,"uid":46231,"like":154,"dislike":17,"score":137,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T16:41:57.000Z","msg":"女人揸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點建解係要做d自己控制唔到嘅事  剪撚左個牌佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1914a704781acf8b99a6d91cb8dca5ddd817927","tid":498344,"uid":26602,"like":124,"dislike":3,"score":121,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T16:53:11.000Z","msg":"4條線咁闊都可以轉唔到炒車<br />\n條女個牌點考返嚟"},{"pid":"8346e903cad06303bc21553ffca54715af87b157","tid":498344,"uid":47674,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T16:55:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢當年點考窄路掉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係停車場轉出馬路過對面線，仲易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39a546a59d86d231fd4171adff8405c8a96b82ad","tid":498344,"uid":38539,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T17:51:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc3e0f53c2066505bf84f374469a10ee3f7b7df9","tid":498344,"uid":12591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:21:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad246eecc9e57928d1091a8527a632da205a5993","tid":498344,"uid":22566,"like":85,"dislike":0,"score":85,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:47:03.000Z","msg":"技驚四座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3fe71bc5aa9b63f6ad9f76e7a7e018c164f140c","tid":498344,"uid":35468,"like":79,"dislike":0,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:48:57.000Z","msg":"其實畀呢啲人揸車好危險"},{"pid":"ce0